olemus|RFA]] has succeeded, and he is now an [[WB:ADMIN|administrator]]. ;Wikibooks and Wikijunior Logos :Logo submissions will be accepted until about the 15th of March, at which point we'll begin the next phase. The process is outlined at [[m:Wikibooks/Logo|Meta]]. }} {{dynamic navigation|expand=yes|title=January 2008|body= ;NPOV Checking :[[User:Laleena|Laleena]] is heading up an effort to review all our [[:Category:NPOV disputes|modules]] tagged as [[WB:NPOV|NPOV]] violations. All users are invited to help improve these modules to comply with policy. ;[[Special:Userrights]] :This new special page allows user rights using a single interface. The previous methods to [[Special:Makebot|make bots]] and [[Special:Makesysop|make sysops]] will be depreciated once work on the user interface is complete. :The underlying schema also allows more modular user rights. Users may now request the [[Help:Editing#Rollback|rollbacker]] and [[Wikibooks:New page patrol|patroller]] rights at [[Wikibooks:Requests for permissions]]. This allows [[Wikibooks:Dealing with vandalism|vandal fighters]] and new page patrollers to spread the work out over a greater number of people. See [[Wikibooks:User rights]] and [[Wikibooks:Reading room/General#Rollback and Patroller Rights]] for details.
