== Parametric Equations ==
{{question-answer|question=1. Find parametric equations describing the line segment from ''P''(0,0) to ''Q''(7,17).|answer={{noprint|1=''x''=7''t'' and ''y''=17''t'', where 0 ≤ ''t'' ≤ 1}}}}
{{question-answer|question=2. Find parametric equations describing the line segment from <math>P(x_1,y_1)</math> to <math>Q(x_2,y_2)</math>.|answer={{noprint|1=<math>x=x_1 + (x_2-x_1)t \mbox{ and } y=y_1 + (y_2-y_1)t, \mbox{ where } 0 \leq t \leq 1</math>}}}}
{{question-answer|question=3. Find parametric equations describing the ellipse centered at the origin with major axis of length 6 along the ''x''-axis and the minor axis of length 3 along the ''y''-axis, generated clockwise.|answer={{noprint|1=<math>x=3\cos(-t),\ y=1.5\sin(-t)</math>}}}}

