{{question-answer|question=545. <math>\mathbf F = \langle x, 2y, 3z \rangle</math>, <math>S</math> is the boundary of the region between the cylinders <math>x^2+y^2=1</math> and <math>x^2+y^2=4</math> and cut off by planes <math>z=0</math> and <math>z=8</math> |answer={{noprint|1= <math>144\pi</math>}}}}


